      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARSET (1) improving gelding with his hoof on the till at start five. Will relish the blinkers second-up after sitting on the speed from the wide gate with a narrow second over 1250m at Newcastle. Gets the gun run today and can put these away around the tight Wyong track. OBSIDIAN DREAM (7) big improver second-up from the low draw with a gritty on-pace fourth over 1200m at Gosford. Key jockey change and ready for this trip. NONNO'S POWER (3) yet to draw a decent gate in two starts back and today is no different. Snagged back early and made some ground in the straight with a plugging seventh over 1250m at Newcastle. Can run into the money today. GONG GIRL (9) was well supported first-up when no match for the handy Mrs Maree with a plugging third over 1200m at this track. Looks to have further improvement and is ready for this trip and further now.",
